text.tspan: Need something to throw at your kids and let them develop creativity? We have
ready-to-play projects for non-makers and beginners at all ages, including paper-craft
airplanes, paper gliders, 3D pen stencils, hands-on training for digital graphic manipulation,
We are located at Street 20, Wat Bo area, near National Highway 6 and Wat Bo street,
between Babel Guesthouse and Happy Guesthouse. For interactive direction, visit our website.
